channel.title: War Head - Tornait
channel.description:
New song out. Called War Head. https://soundcloud.com/tornait-jaybird/war-head
Fair warning, little to no automation on this song, if you’re into that. However, I put an equal amount of love, passion and attention into every song I make. This time I wanted to make something a little bit more... high-energy.
Anyways... what genre is this song? I do know I wanted something with absolutely slammin drums, and an anthem-like lead to it... am I becoming Bastille/Imagine Dragons?
Huh. Well... please give me feedback. Your time is very valuable to me, and it gives me a huge motivational boost with every post. Thank you, and hope you enjoy the track!
